tps://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/Th%E1%BA%A5m-vi%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-f6ACw6dnutZomkB8WqqtfQ">Thấm viên xuân - Thưởng xuân từ - 沁園春－賞春詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/author-Pf4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A5t-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BA%A5t-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Chung-minh-ph%E1%BB%A7-thu%E1%BB%B7-l%C3%A2u-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-zboxsB8hHrnertA5CpBzvw">Thất nguyệt nhất nhật đề Chung minh phủ thuỷ lâu kỳ 1 - 七月一日題終明府水樓其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/V%C5%A9-y-kh%C3%BAc/poem-32dhqqYcnCKz44hx_9cxAg">Vũ y khúc - 舞衣曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/author-VkIfi7DKP2f1cM8JZZP8yA">Ôn Đình Quân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Xa-l%C3%A2n-3/poem-wtZNPqzmmj5cJinBMiGDkA">Xa lân 3 - 車鄰 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
